STATE of North Carolina
v.
Fred Norris MARTIN, Jr. No. 665P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Kelly D. Miller, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Fred Norris Martin, Jr. Sueanna P. Sumpter, Assistant Attorney General, Jerry Wilson, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 2nd day of December 2005 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th day of January 2006."
